Femi Fani-Kayode, former Aviation Minister, has expressed his resentment for those currently governing Nigeria. Fani-Kayode said Nigeria was currently governed by “cow lovers and pedophiles.” In a series of tweets on Tuesday, the former Minister also described those governing Nigeria as religious bigots and ethnic supremacists.
He stated that Nigeria had been led by inferiors as a result of the decision of a lot of people not to participate in politics. He wrote: “One of the penalties for refusing to participate in politics is that you end up being governed by your inferiors – Plato “There is no greater evidence of this truism than the Nigeria condition. “We are being governed by cow-lovers, pedophiles, religious bigots and ethnic supremacists.” Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.